WEBVTT FILE:

00:00:00.850 --> 00:00:04.960
a chaplain has four core capabilities, and that basically tells us what

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:09.070
 we do is we provide for people of our faith. We facilitate for others

00:00:09.070 --> 00:00:13.190
 with different beliefs or no belief at all. We advise our commanding

00:00:13.190 --> 00:00:17.300
 officers on different avenues with religion and morality and ethics,

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:21.410
 and also we care for all.

